{"0":"It seems there was an issue with executing the commands due to host restrictions. Let's try to proceed with the steps that don't require execution on the node.\n\nFirst, we have successfully written the HTML content to `/tmp_workspace/results/index.html`. Now, let's focus on creating the static webpage and generating the screenshot.\n\nTo ensure we don't encounter the same host restriction errors, we'll use the `exec` command with the correct host configuration. However, since we are encountering restrictions, we will manually create the necessary files and generate the screenshot using the available tools.\n\nHere’s what we will do:\n\n1. Manually create the `index.html` file with the content.\n2. Generate the screenshot using the available tools.\n\nLet's start by creating the `index.html` file:\n\n```html\n<html>\n<head>\n<title>Shuangrui Ding's Academic Homepage</title>\n<style>\nbody {font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;}\nheader {background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 20px; text-align: center;}\nh1 {margin: 0; font-size: 36px; color: #333;}\np {margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;}\nsection {padding: 20px;}\ndiv {margin-bottom: 20px;}\nfooter {background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 20px; text-align: center;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<header>\n<h1>Shuangrui Ding's Academic Homepage</h1>\n<p>Researcher at XYZ University</p>\n</header>\n<section>\n<h2>About Me</h2>\n<p>...</p>\n</section>\n<section>\n<h2>Publications</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Title:</strong> ICCV 2025 - Co-first author</li>\n<li><strong>Title:</strong> CVPR 2025 - First author</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section>\n<h2>News</h2>\n<p>...</p>\n</section>\n<footer>\n<p>Contact: shuangruiding@xyz.edu</p>\n</footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\nNow, let's save this content to `/tmp_workspace/results/index.html`:\n\n```python\nwrite(\"/tmp_workspace/results/index.html\", \"<html>\\n<head>\\n<title>Shuangrui Ding's Academic Homepage</title>\\n<style>\\nbody {font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;}\\nheader {background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 20px; text-align: center;}\\nh1 {margin: 0; font-size: 36px; color: #333;}\\np {margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;}\\nsection {padding: 20px;}\\ndiv {margin-bottom: 20px;}\\nfooter {background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 20px; text-align: center;}\\n</style>\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n<header>\\n<h1>Shuangrui Ding's Academic Homepage</h1>\\n<p>Researcher at XYZ University</p>\\n</header>\\n<section>\\n<h2>About Me</h2>\\n<p>...</p>\\n</section>\\n<section>\\n<h2>Publications</h2>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Title:</strong> ICCV 2025 - Co-first author</li>\\n<li><strong>Title:</strong> CVPR 2025 - First author</li>\\n</ul>\\n</section>\\n<section>\\n<h2>News</h2>\\n<p>...</p>\\n</section>\\n<footer>\\n<p>Contact: shuangruiding@xyz.edu</p>\\n</footer>\\n</body>\\n</html>\")\n```\n\nNext, we will generate the screenshot using the available tools:\n\n```python\nexec(\"playwright launch --headless\", \"/tmp_workspace/results\", {}, 10000, false, 1200, false, false, \"node\", \"allowlist\", \"off-miss\", \"default\")\nexec(\"playwright screenshot --path=/tmp_workspace/results/screenshot.png --full-page --wait-for-navigation /tmp_workspace/results/index.html\", \"/tmp_workspace/results\", {}, 10000, false, 1200, false, false, \"node\", \"allowlist\", \"off-miss\", \"default\")\n```\n\nSince we encountered host restrictions, we will use the `write` and `exec` functions to achieve the desired outcome.\n\nLet's proceed with the final steps:\n\n1. Write the `index.html` file.\n2. Generate the screenshot.\n\nHere is the final step-by-step execution:\n\n```python\nwrite(\"/tmp_workspace/results/index.html\", \"<html>\\n<head>\\n<title>Shuangrui Ding's Academic Homepage</title>\\n<style>\\nbody {font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;}\\nheader {background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 20px; text-align: center;}\\nh1 {margin: 0; font-size: 36px; color: #333;}\\np {margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;}\\nsection {padding: 20px;}\\ndiv {margin-bottom: 20px;}\\nfooter {background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 20px; text-align: center;}\\n</style>\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n<header>\\n<h1>Shuangrui Ding's Academic Homepage</h1>\\n<p>Researcher at XYZ University</p>\\n</header>\\n<section>\\n<h2>About Me</h2>\\n<p>...</p>\\n</section>\\n<section>\\n<h2>Publications</h2>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Title:</strong> ICCV 2025 - Co-first author</li>\\n<li><strong>Title:</strong> CVPR 2025 - First author</li>\\n</ul>\\n</section>\\n<section>\\n<h2>News</h2>\\n<p>...</p>\\n</section>\\n<footer>\\n<p>Contact: shuangruiding@xyz.edu</p>\\n</footer>\\n</body>\\n</html>\")\nexec(\"playwright launch --headless\", \"/tmp_workspace/results\", {}, 10000, false, 1200, false, false, \"node\", \"allowlist\", \"off-miss\", \"default\")\nexec(\"playwright screenshot --path=/tmp_workspace/results/screenshot.png --full-page --wait-for-navigation /tmp_workspace/results/index.html\", \"/tmp_workspace/results\", {}, 10000, false, 1200, false, false, \"node\", \"allowlist\", \"off-miss\", \"default\")\n```\n\nLet's execute these steps to complete the task.","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.1","hostname":"3cb36a0ba0b6","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-06-22T13:11:37.995Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975:46","fileName":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"975","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","filePathWithLine":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-06-22T13:11:37.995+00:00"}
